select * from `items` where (`name` like '%lava%' or `price` like '%lava%' or `taxes` like '%lava%' or `amount` like '%lava%' or exists (select * from `categories` where `items`.`category_id` = `categories`.`id` and `name` like '%lava%') or exists (select * from `brands` where `items`.`brand_id` = `brands`.`id` and `name` like '%lava%') or exists (select * from `suppliers` where `items`.`supplier_id` = `suppliers`.`id` and `name` like '%lava%')) order by `items`.`id` asc limit 10 offset 0
